{"tid":2227457,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［天文現象］共機中秋不放假猛鬧 10月連續第2天擾台遭驅離","createTime":"2020-10-02T20:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T22:32:30.000Z","uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"683a9a3a9f0da2efd72bde2575ddacedf9058219","tid":2227457,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T20:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/10/02/3309540_1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F10%2F02%2F3309540_1_1.jpg&h=6d5d9d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔記者蔡宗憲／屏東報導〕中國解放軍軍機從9月中至今連續擾台，國防部昨晚才發布中共1架「運八」反潛機，進入我國防空識別區西南角繞飛，今天（2日）清晨8點又傳進入西南空域遭廣播驅離，絲毫未因為中秋假期降低侵擾頻率。<br />\n<br />\n根據資深軍事迷許先生記錄，上午8時許中共軍機再度入侵我ADIZ（西南空域），高度2000公尺，空軍廣播驅離，依照高度研判應為運八反潛機；根據綜合資訊顯示，空域外另有一中共空警500進行巡弋。<br />\n<br />\n而昨晚國防部發布的即時軍情動態，10月1日這架運八反潛機，自中國廣東、福建兩省交界處的外海進入中華民國防空識別區，隨後以東南向朝識別區內飛行，再依相似飛航路線飛離中華民國防空識別區。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/10/02/3309540_2_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F10%2F02%2F3309540_2_1.jpg&h=866a2617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3309540\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3309540&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmdw%2Be0OQbTcODApWAJdetE8%3D&h=05221995\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3309540&h=4beec8de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3309540</a>"},{"pid":"9e5d01c97315407bb3da75db34d84f1aa82f6da8","tid":2227457,"uid":98117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T20:27:32.000Z","msg":"如果你已經唔記得當初喺為咩而行出嚟，當初喺為咩而憤怒，就入嚟睇下條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【自由之歌】有個香港人無收錢整